<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA11">
<l>vāyavaṉai yallatu vāḻttātu kaiyulakan</l>
<l>tāyavaṉai yallatu tāntoḻāp – pēymulainañ</l>
<l>cūṇāka vuṇṭā ṉuruvoṭu pērallāṟ</l>
<l>kāṇākaṇ kēḷā cevi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mouth will praise none but him; the hands will fold for</l>
<l>none but him who stretched over the world; except for the name and the form</l>
<l>of him who ate as food the poison from the breast of the demoness</l>
<l>the eyes won’t see, the ears won’t hear.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
